OL,3,CAbuse survivors encouraged to come
OL,4,Cforward before compensation deadline
OL,6,FThere are calls to extend the deadline
OL,7,Ffor applications to a redress scheme
OL,8,Ffor survivors of historical
OL,9,Finstitutional abuse.
OL,11,FThose affected have been able to seek
OL,12,Fcompensation since 2020, but it has
OL,13,Fbeen claimed that not enough was done
OL,14,Fto promote the programme.
OL,16,FIn 2022 Stormont ministers offered a
OL,17,Fpublic apology to survivors of
OL,18,Fhistorical institutional abuse.
