OL,3,CAbuse survivors encouraged to come
OL,4,Cforward before compensation deadline
OL,6,F"If you're a married woman or a
OL,7,Fmarried man and you haven't told your
OL,8,Ffamily that you were in these
OL,9,Finstitutions it's very hard," said Ms
OL,10,FRogers-Moloney.
OL,12,FShe added: "I really, really would
OL,13,Fencourage them to come forward."
OL,15,FFor Cyril Glass, memories of his time
OL,16,Fspent at Rathgael training school are
OL,17,Fstill painful.
OL,19,FHe also wants a rethink on the
OL,20,Fdeadline for compensation applications.
