OL,3,CAbuse survivors encouraged to come
OL,4,Cforward before compensation deadline
OL,6,F"Redress was set up in April 2020,
OL,7,Fthere was a big public campaign
OL,8,Fsupposed to happen worldwide then
OL,9,FCOVID kicked in, so that didn't
OL,10,Fhappen."
OL,12,FMr Glass said the Executive Office
OL,13,Flater told him it no longer had the
OL,14,Ffunds available for the campaign.
OL,16,FUTV has contacted the Executive Office
OL,17,Ffor a response.
